### Enviar código para cadastro
POST http://localhost:8080/verificacao-email/cadastro/enviar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "20242ireads0004@ifba.edu.br"
}

### Validar código e criar cliente
POST http://localhost:8080/verificacao-email/cadastro/validar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "20242ireads0004@ifba.edu.br",
  "codigo": "755565",
  "cliente": {
    "nome": "Cliente Teste Email",
    "email": "20242ireads0004@ifba.edu.br",
    "senha": "12345678",
    "telefone": "",
    "cpf": ""
  }
}

### Enviar link para recuperação de senha
POST http://localhost:8080/verificacao-email/senha/enviar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "20242ireads0004@ifba.edu.br"
}

### Redefinir senha com token
POST http://localhost:8080/verificacao-email/senha/redefinir
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "2e5f4b1d-18d4-43b7-9ff6-80aa9de5b0ad",
  "novaSenha": "novaSenha123"
}